{"word":"G4637 - σκηνόω - skēnóō - skay-no'-o - Dwell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκηνόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">skēnóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">skay-no'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dwell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாசம் பண்ணு, வாசமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to fix one's tabernacle, have one's tabernacle, abide (or live) in a tabernacle (or tent), tabernacle"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4636 - σκῆνος - skēnos - skay'-nos/4636\">G4636</a>; to <i>tent</i> or <i>encamp</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>occupy</i> (as a mansion) or (specifically) to <i>reside</i> (as God did in the Tabernacle of old, a symbol fo protection and communion): - dwell.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1981/1981\">G1981</a>, <a href=\"#/G2681/2681\">G2681</a>, <a href=\"#/G4633/4633\">G4633</a>, <a href=\"#/G4634/4634\">G4634</a>, <a href=\"#/G4635/4635\">G4635</a>, <a href=\"#/G4636/4636\">G4636</a>, <a href=\"#/G4637/4637\">G4637</a>, <a href=\"#/G4638/4638\">G4638</a>"}]}